<p>æ­£æ€åˆ†å¸ƒ$p(x)=\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}\sigma}e^{-\dfrac{(x-\mu)^2}{2\sigma^2}}$,$X\thicksim N(\mu,\sigma^2)$.</p>

<p>è‹¥$X\thicksim N(\mu,\sigma^2),Y=\dfrac{X-\mu}{\sigma}\thicksim N(0,1)$ï¼Œä»¥åŠ$3\sigma$åŸç†</p>

